@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### =========================================
### CQRS WRITE SIDE (Commands)
### =========================================

### Create a new order (Triggers Saga)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: req-order-1

{
  "orderId": "order_101",
  "customerId": "cust_101",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "prod_101",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### =========================================
### CQRS READ SIDE (Queries)
### =========================================

### Get an order status and details (Materialized View)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/order_101
